===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{italbrac|intransitive}} To offer [[illicit]] sex with a third party; to [[pimp]].
# {{italbrac|intransitive}} To [[tempt]] with, to [[appeal]] to ([[improper]] [[motivations]] etc.); to assist in the gratification of.
# ''His latest speech simply '''panders''' to the worst instincts of the electorate.''

